widgets_values: In a bleak near-future cityscape, towering holographic adverts loom over crumbling slums. Cybernetic enhancements clash with malnourished flesh. Trillionaires float in luxury pods while below, hackers and cybercriminals weave through the desperate masses. Gargantuan drones patrol as protestors scream against biotech homogenization and ecocide. Amidst this hopeless tableau, a lone figure clings to dreams of a better world, illuminated by flickering neon hope.
